{"tid":1298150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝備] 應對臭蟹面罩疑問","createTime":"2019-07-08T19:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:00:40.000Z","uid":231905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7fad16fcd9d75a670127d103f90c8287cc7d662b","tid":1298150,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:31:18.000Z","msg":"早排炒蟹啲味那到口水鼻涕噴出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頂唔順去咗買個面罩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2HVxK3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2HVxK3.png&h=55f8f2ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買咗3200面罩同3301嗰隻毒罐<br />\n但係上網爬文有人話臭蟹味係粉末，有人又話有機氣體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3301個罐淨係for有機氣體，似乎冇嗰啲咩濾棉擋粉末<br />\n唔知有冇實戰過炒蟹高手分享下心得<br />\n究竟係要濾棉定係濾罐<br />\n我就咁3200+3301會唔會仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3177a0822d61f1a1e6617ce13461ce6cdb9c03a8","tid":1298150,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:33:54.000Z","msg":"有冇大師分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223aad40b09949f13703fa767deda5ce4df5f71b","tid":1298150,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:36:48.000Z","msg":"求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032e2cdb942588e2eae99bce542f982bf6e2c530","tid":1298150,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:39:18.000Z","